| **Tenebress Territory**   | Region             | Battleground against fire god; site of Pindars’ second victorious campaign.                         |

### **FACTIONS / NATIONS:**

| Faction                | Leader               | Headquarters          | Purpose / Focus                                                                   |
| ---------------------- | -------------------- | --------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
